Exercise and Heart rate
-----------------------

[[node-181]]
Tue, 23/02/2010 - 21:08 — mnd22

Introduction

Public summary: 

Why does your heat beat faster after exercise? Come and find out why in
this demonstration where you are the subject.

Public visibility: 

Demonstrators

Teachers

General public

When you exercise your heart beats faster!

